            "title": "金價在5,000美元上方保持上漲 「貶值交易」捲土重來",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"金價在5,000美元上方保持上漲 「貶值交易」捲土重來\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FhyIm8qvh.WJ4wkwHJ5OoA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/2020-03/2aaf1a70-6527-11ea-bffc-78902fb3167f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">金價在5,000美元上方保持上漲 「貶值交易」捲土重來</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
