        {
            "title": "日圓匯率與日本國債動盪交織 高市早苗政府在大選前面臨市場考驗",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/d8DL1zP.G4LN3aHIoFe8dg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1b692669608f2690ee7b6b7ffb142983\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 日本首相高市早苗啟動競選活動，首要目標是確保2月8日投票順利進行，避免金融市場劇烈波動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據一位財務省知情官員透露，隨著市場壓力不斷加劇，如何做到這一點讓上任僅三個月的高市政府和日本央行頭疼不已。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位官員表示，問題在於，任何壓低債券殖利率的舉措都會導致日圓進一步貶值，從而推高輸入型通膨並加大升息壓力。若出手干預支撐日圓，又可能打壓股市上漲勢頭，而股市已是為數不多能在選舉日前為高市政府臉上添光的市場指標之一。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2a0f4a4d-ddb9-3e51-a6e8-6beb0e4f8435-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"高市早苗攝影：David Mareuil/Anadolu Agency/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ogMtUPqVjVYhp.JHipzg_g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ce1063c2376a7950c617768bd5c32c7e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">高市早苗攝影：David Mareuil/Anadolu Agency/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位官員表示，無論政府採取什麼措施，都無法解決所有問題。目前，當局正試圖通過強硬表態並借助美國的一點幫助來應對市場波動。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">財務省未立即回應置評請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">競選活動周二正式拉開帷幕，高市早苗力圖借由此次選舉鞏固執政聯盟在眾議院的多數席位。周末進行的民調顯示，儘管她的支持率略有下滑，但總體仍保持在較高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：日本選戰將拉開大幕 高市早苗支持率略有下滑</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上周晚些時候，市場猜測美國和日本可能在外匯市場採取了協調行動，這提振了日圓匯率。但迄今並無跡象顯示當局實際開展了干預。日本財務大臣片山皋月和美國財長貝森特喊話日本債券市場冷靜，暫時緩解了殖利率的上升壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Lombard Odier高級宏觀策略師Homin Lee表示，一旦選舉後新內閣組建並通過年度預算，在管理日圓匯率和日債殖利率之間實現適當平衡會變得更容易一些。他指出，目前的關鍵在於未來兩到三周內維持穩定局面。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「日本政府可能希望利用政策工具，同時穩定日債殖利率和日圓匯率，」他說。「顯然，要同時實現這兩個目標並不容易。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan’s Leader Faces Balancing Act on Yen Ahead of Election</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 John Cheng、Sakura Murakami.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%93%E5%8C%AF%E7%8E%87%E8%88%87%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5%E5%8B%95%E7%9B%AA%E4%BA%A4%E7%B9%94-%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%82%E6%97%A9%E8%8B%97%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E5%89%8D%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E8%80%83%E9%A9%97-015118565.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-27 10:33:01",
